1. *Kaže* da će biti sunčano sutra. (He says it will be sunny tomorrow.)

2. On mi je *kaže* da je dobro. (He told me it was good.)

3. Da li ti je ona *kaže*? (Did she tell you?)

4. Ona *kaže* da će se vratiti za par dana. (She says she'll be back in a few days.)

5. *Kaže* se da je ona prilično uspešna. (It is said that she is quite successful.)

6. Nisam bio siguran šta da radim, ali on mi je *kaže* da se opustim. (I wasn't sure what to do, but he told me to relax.)